===Alternative forms===
Note that there is no line above [[生]] in Japanese {{w|shinjitai}}. A CJK compatibility ideograph (U+F9DC) exists for the {{w|kyūjitai}} form of {{ja-l|隆}} which has an extra line above [[生]]. Due to {{w|Han unification}}, the Chinese form (with line above [[生]]) and Japanese form (without line) are encoded under the same codepoint. The character [[𨺓]] (U+28E93) exists for the Chinese form with no line above [[生]].

